values:
Well, I have my new journal.. the username is goosiegoo (I went with something that wouldn't age as much. Hasn't aged yet, so..)

So, i shall continue my journal updatings there! I'm guessing it'll be... exactly the same sort of stuff as this journal!

Well, Bye! Ciao! Seeya! On the flip side! Gotta fly! Auf Wiedersehen!! Farewell!

I've decided to make a new lj.. mm. 

All the hormonal bitching about rather stupid things sort of pisses me off, and i thought l'd start a new lj, seeing as l've changed so much. 
Not that the new lj is going to be all hormonal tantrum-less.. just hopefully about bigger things when i do bitch. 

I'm not gonna delete this one or anything, it'll still be there for the records. :p Like an old diary..

Anywho, i need a new name.. suggestions? I would go with the 'goosiegoo' just cos it's my.. account name thingy, and l'd like a new lj to have a name that i won't grow out of too fast... haven't grown out of goosiegoo yet.. :p

Unless i can think of something really witty. Heh. 

Anywho, i shall inform you when l've made it.. so you can all befriend me.

Well, Yr 11's started.. *scowl* :p It's not too bad.. but the heat REALLY makes it crap-tacular. 
I have some pretty good teachers.. and all that. :p Cept I'm in no classes with zoe! *growls*

Oh.. and l have 3 classes worth of homework. *rolls eyes* :p I didn't have ANY homework in yr 10. prrrrf. 

But.. we found out yesterday that we get to go to onstage with Sheahan! Woooooo! I'm so excited! Excursion with Syd-o. *dances* You better be there at the same time as us Elly! What's your uniform like.. mine's black and white. :p But Steph's is different and there'll be more of those. :p

Yay! Hyper on the bus at 5am! Wooooot! 

Alright. Well l'm gonna stop now. 

Woooot!

Wow.. l had a big yr 11 freak out.. but it's ok. I'll forget about it. Cept tomorrow when l go get my uniform *rasps for breath* Alright.. well.. l was real mad cos l found out that instead of going to blue bay on the..like.. 14th we have to go one the 16th. And eve though that doesn't seem like much, it means that when l come back l'll only have like 2 days until school. Dunno if l can prepare myself for that. But.. l'll just have to do heaps of stuff with my friends before l go away. Anyway.. l don't really wanna talk about that anymore. :p I mean, rennie is probably scareder.. she's going to uni! eep. Anyway.. l thought l'd leave you with some pics. :p Cos l have to go to bed. Umm.. l can't be bothered Well.. g'bye! :p

Yay! Christmas! I can't really be bothered talking about my christmas.. but it was fun. :p

I haven't really been updating much.. cos l haven't been on lj.. and prrf. I can't be bothered. :p I've been doing a bit of bebo-ing. And nooo.. l'm not abandoning LJ.. i haven't really been doing anything bloggy on bebo.. but all the people from my school are on bebo so l'm making friends. :p Which means l can definatly not talk about the sort of stuff l talk about on this lj. :p If someone stumbled across it.. *screeches*

Well.. l need sleep. But MERRY CHRISTMAS EVERYONE! Rollerblading is trendy. :p

No one read my last post. :p Or.. no one commented. I say.. go comment now! But l couldn't help doing that.. LJ... thing.. that Elly had on her lj. You know.. with the.. Year in Review Meme: Take the first sentence (or 2) from the first post of each month of 2005. That's your year in review. exclude private posts unless the sentences are really juicy. January: "l'm going away everyone, so seeya on the flip side... Holiday roooooaaaadddd...." February: "Heya. I haven't spoked to you in ages. And l can't really say anything now. Do you like my colours? Of course you do. " March: "I'm starting to wonder why l should update when no one reads it!! *cries hysterically*. Alright. I'm over it. " (God.. i hope my life starts getting more interesting) April: "Here are some pictures l drew..... With a pencil.." May: "Hello All, long time no update. Well, I'm staying home today so l thought l might go and update good ol' livejournal. " (wow.. I'm so interesting..) June: "EEEE! It's raunung *sigh* and l woke up today and immediatly wanted to read order of the phoenix..so l read 2 chapters before l felt like writing fan fiction." (wow..it's raunung.. that doesn't happen often..) July: "everyone seems to do that..'linky' thingy all the time. :p Like..thinking to big text in their joournal - but l don't know how. So here it is. :p Quizzy Thingy. " (next year l'm noting what l start my first updates of the month with and making them more interesting) "I wanted to add this even though it isn't the frst: Oh, and i read HARRY POTTER. mmhmm. Won't say anything...might be too dangerous. But l will say..hat l can't put it in words. :p wooo!" (makes Harry Potter seem like an un-big deal. WELL IT WASN'T) August: "Tommorow is just so busy! - My HUGE science assignment is due *chokes* - I have a maths test and l can't remember anything its on..." September: "Today was definatly a day for freaking out. Was up till 12 last night making a farewell Ren and Dad card. Wok eup and was very tried and emotional...." October: "I want a Mr Darcy." November: "I finished exams! *punches air* And.. I got my dress and my shoes! *punches air* And I haven't updated in AGES. *doesn't punch air*" December: (I felt like posting most of it. *swoons*) "I'VE SEEN HARRY POTTER AND THE GOBLET OF FIRE!!!!!!!!!!!! IT WAS EXCELLENT!!!!!!!!! BEST ONE YET!!!!!!!!!!!!! DIDN'T MAKE ME DISSAPOINTED!!!!!!!!!!!! I WANT ROBERT PATTINSON (CEDRIC DIGGORY) SOOOOOO BAD!!!!!!!!!!! DAN WITHOUT A SHIRT!!!! BEST THING EVER!!!!!!!!" Well.. that was.. amusing. Seems like the year went really quickly. But then again, this year wasn't a 'update lj' year. I was the year of the roleplay. Yes yes.The year of grace having no life. yes yes. The year of Grace turning into Lorelei. Yes Yes.

Ok.. so l got my results.. brace yourself. :p

English: 88%
Science: 90%
History: 82%
Geography: 83%
Maths: 81%


YAHHHH!!

I was very happy. 1 band 6 and 4 band fives.. which is actually better than a lot of the brainy kids. :p Cept like Kiri and Rob. Who got 3 band 6's. *mutters*

Anyway... YAH!! The only one l was a bit angered by was English. :p I wish i'd gotten higher.. even though thats stupid. Well Zoe beat me! :p And she's the maths one.. I'm the english one. :p But still, she did very well. 2 band 6's 2 band 5's and 1 band 4. I was very happy that she got a band 6 in maths, she deserved it. And as usual our scores manage to equal out to about the same average. :p 

Anywho..

YAH!!!

I was also happy that my SC report says that l have drama for 200 hours with an A. :p Cos i got straight a's in drama..

YAHH!!

Holiday roooaaaaddddd holiday rrrrrrrrooooaaaaadddddd.

YAH!

I GOT NINETY PERCENT IN SCIENCE!!!!!!!! *runs around like a mad man* I was soooo happy! If l wanted one thing in the school certificate.. it was to do good in science. I hoped so much that I'd get a band six.. not that I knew if l would... BUT I DID! I'm soooooo happy! And Syd rocks because of her enthusiasm. And Mr Adams rocks because I wouldn't have gotten it if l hadn't have been in his class these last two months... and he said he was proud of me. He's one of those people that you really don't want to dissapoint. Our class average was 85%.. that's damn good for the class average. And Kiri got 96%, top of the year.. she's so smart.. :p I'll find out my other scores on friday.. (I keep worrying that Mr Adams told me the wrong score. :p) Everyone's started getting theirs from the office but l said l didn't want to until friday.. HUZZAH!!!!! I'M HAPPY!! Hope l get good in english.. don't think I'll do very well in geography at all..

I'VE SEEN HARRY POTTER AND THE GOBLET OF FIRE!!!!!!!!!!!!

IT WAS EXCELLENT!!!!!!!!! BEST ONE YET!!!!!!!!!!!!! DIDN'T MAKE ME DISSAPOINTED!!!!!!!!!!!!

I WANT ROBERT PATTINSON (CEDRIC DIGGORY) SOOOOOO BAD!!!!!!!!!!!

DAN WITHOUT A SHIRT!!!! BEST THING EVER!!!!!!!!

AHHHHHH!!!!!!

*faints*

Ok.. I have a lot of formal pics to post.. but compared to the amount i actually have.. you should feel lucky. :p My shoes!: Me, full: Close up of Me: My hair!: Beki tried to make me look like an angel. :p Kristen, Rosemary, Zoe and Me. Zoe's hair is straight!! I just posted this cos it looks like Zoe is giving me a death stare. :p I don't remember this.. but is it just me, or did l just tell a funny joke? :p You don't know Shaye.. but here's me and Shaye! (Gymnastics teacher) Zoe and Rosemary: The dancefloor: This pic just amused me: So..eee! :p I have sooo many pictures, but l decided l wouldn't show you the ones with.. people you've never heard of. I want to see Steph's when.. she has her formal!

Heh. Well last night was the formal.. it was FUN! :p Cept I was sick with a cold.. and still am.. and am sort of.. sleepy. 

Anyway, everyone looked stunn-ing, and zoe had her hair straightened! And I can't remember the rest. Hehe. Lorelei wore a dress *gasp* She's like a real tomboy and I've never seen her in a skirt or dress.. and she told us she was gonna wear a suit.. but then she wore this pretty blue dress. But it was really lame when Katie saw her and started crying. I mean.. I was cool but not that exciting.. :p 

Anyway, i can't talk now.. but i'll post pictures tomorrow!

*Holds on to fifteen yearold pole*

No, no.. it's alright. I had a quite good last day of being fifteen.. until this arvo. But in gymnastics, alll year l've had those mental problems where my legs won't let me jump :p and l've really wanted to do a handspring (you know l found out that zoe thought a backward summersault was a backflip. Thats just common sense to me!) but the creepy thing about handsprings is that you have to jump..and then flllyyy, land on your hands on the mat and then land on your feet. :p Well, yes, my mind hasn't been letting me jump onto my hands cos the last time l did it l like..dived. Onto my neck. 
Anyway, so today Shaye says "No Grace! You're going to do it! And you're going to jump and land on your hands and land on your feet!" 

AND I DID!!! YAH!!!

I used to be able to do it.. and l can do it again! Incredible achievement for grace, mentally. 

So l decided that was a rockin' way to leave my 15 yearoldness behind, and also decided that l was growing..mentally. :p 

But then I got home. :( And Buttercup (one of the cows) has been really crappy..like hasn't been able to walk much, and dad called the vet while l was out and the vet put Buttercup down. :( And she's getting taken away tomorrow morning.. what a nice way to wake up on my birthday. I've requested that they let me sleep in until it's over. 
And I just saw Horney (don't laugh at the name.. she has horns.) sitting there..looking all alone. :( And it was saddd. The vet said she isn't very well either.. *pouts*
But they're pretty old cows.. and they've had a good life of.. eating grass... grazing.. etc.

So.. Blah.

Oh, and my camera hasn't arrived so l prob won't get to take pics on my birthday. :( But thats alright..l'll live.

Gooodbyeeee Fifteen!

I finished exams! *punches air*

And.. I got my dress and my shoes! *punches air*

And I haven't updated in AGES. *doesn't punch air*

And everyone's like 'You can get your L's soon!!" And I'm like I DON'T WANT TO! Thats way to grown up. 

And... hmm.. I think l'll go to the movies tonight. 

I have a pic of me in my dress...but l don't exactly look as GLAMEROUS as l will at the formal. :p But it's not on my computer

I'm getting a camera for my birthday. Woo-hoot. Ohhh the memories!!!

Elly l demand that you come to my party. 

Should l have a theme? I think..yes.

Um.. anything else?
Oh.. a while a go Rosemary had a fit and started hallucinating and went back to hospital. But thats all over now. 
Cept people think she's a druggo. hehee. I thought it was amusing. 
She got crushed twice at the disco. hmm.. 

Disco was fun. Danced in the mosh pit which had heaps of yr 11's. 

Woo-hoot.

Well..l went away..and now l'm back. Huzzah!
I don't feel like talking about the trip for...ever, l'm too tired. But it was very fun, place was nice, l developed a cool, ugly and nerdy smile. :p Ehehe. and I got an ABBEY ROAD poster! Woooot! No where to put it though...
I'll show pictures later. 

I need to take a st johns wort cos l'm worrying about bird flu. But l'm not anymore... Channel 10 over reacts, and l didn't hear it all anyway. All l heard was bird flu and 150 million so l started freaking out, but supposedly only 50 people have died and vaccinations are cming. but it doesn't help when ur in a class with Mr Adams who rants and rants about how we're well over due for a pandemic. Damnations..

And now l feel like my feet are exposed and people are trying to jab them with needles. Don't know why. Maybe they're bird flu needles?

I think l really am a hypochondriac. 

Sugar Hiccup!

Sorry..was listening to that song. But then l turned it off. Moohaha.Total of good looking boys in the blue mountains: Low.

I feel...random. 

Syd, I think Nikkita knows Josh. :p Cos l got a forward from her that had Josh's email in there too. :p Probably through erin. I realise now that l walked around the show with erin once. :p Ehehe.

I feel..obnoxious...

Well l'm gonna go. 

Shoop Shoop. 

G'Bye!

CREATE YOUR OWN! - or - GET PAID TO TAKE SURVEYS!

Rennie and Dad are back from Egypt! 
It's weird...feels like they didn't go anywhere. 
Rennie had the funniest stories about Dad.. and their tour leader, Emad seems so funny. Hes like a really..big..buff guy that was extremely competitive, and was the national champion in kick boxing and table tennis (hmm) :p but he was all ranting about hwo if anythings wrong he'll go to all lengths to fix it and being really nice. And Dad won a game of pool against him and Emad was soo mad. :p 
But Rennie was going on about how everyone really liked Rennie and Dad, but they didn't know how to react to Dad..cos he was really normal most of the time, and then he'd do something really weird. Like..they were all sitting around and someone said "Oh, this heat is so..stupid.." And Dad stands up really suddenly and says "Well you know whats stupid?!!? Wearing bright purple socks under my sandals!!!" and he takes them off and everyone laughed, and he swimmers on underneath his clothes..and he goes "oh, like that do you!" and takes of his pants with the swimmers underneath..and no one new he had swimmers underneath and l don't know..when rennie told it it was sooo funny...

And l think on of the funniest stories was how he was on a plane, and they give them packs with like..toothpaste, and a a toothbrush, shaving cream, etc...and he was ranting on about how he had used this shaving cream yesterday, and it wa just so refreshing..and he kept patting his face and going 'it was just so refreshing..it must have some sort of asian minerals in it...it was just so refreshing..l mean it took awhile l foam up.." and Rennie finally took the shaving cream he was holding and looked at and goes "oh, you thought this was so refreshing? It's toothpaste.." and he wasn't embarrased at all, he just kept on with the refreshing.. *hysterics* *sigh* He'll never live down shaving with toothpaste...

And what was the other one rennie told me? Funny thing about Dad...sposedly he was really terrible at text messaging, and he'd go out onto the balcony of the hotel saying he was gonna send a text message, and then come back 15 minutes later asking if rennie would send it for him...

But yeah, those were most of the funny stories..

Now, for the most important part..presents! That was a joke. 

I got... this really beautiful, really thin glass perfume bottle, now l need some perfume..
2 egypt-ie necklaces, you know the ones made by..like..peasants and stuff. :p
A proper muslim woman scarf, very pretty..
Some teal beads that are awesome-o
Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets in Arabic!!!!!! to start my collection! :D
Not a present..but l got an egyptian pound for getting rennies bag, and a few malaysian dollars and an american dollar..
and the best one of all..This chain, with a really beautiful..thingy no it, which has...my name engraved in HEIROGLYPHICS!!!! It's so awesome!!!  And it has a heiroglyph alphabet..must write out all your names for you.. 

EEEE!!!


Anyway, l haven't seen pictures yet, but l havce to go study. 

Woot!

Well.. Wobbly (the youngest cow) is really sick, and she can't do anything but lie around... so we think she'll pass on sometime soon. It's really sad...but l can sort of handle the thought of her passing on. What l can't handle is seeing her just lying there not being able to do anything whenever l look out the kitchen window. And l keep remembering how l was the first one to see wobbly after she was born..
I just wish everything crap would stop happening and we could go back into the happy bits..

My school is dull brained. If they think they can get me with a simple "Oh no, we're not doing drama for yr 11 2006. Sorry, ther are only 11 people" Get over it. Fools. I didn't even hear it from an official. Heard it from Ms Mason who was very upset about it. 
Well theres no point being upset. We are doing Yr 11 drama. 
The plan of attack goes as follows:
1. tomorrow Ms Mason talks to the principal about the matter
-if that doesn't work..-
2. Parents of as many people possible who chose drama ring up and complain about it. 
-if that doesn't work..-
3. Todd and I, and prob Rosemary go to Mr Tome and complain. If need be Todd will be on queue to cry. :p I'm not brave enough to cry. 
-if that doens't work..-
4.Then come the petitions, campaigns and protests. Badges, signs, posters, we'll try and go to the news... We say that OHS is discriminating against Drama. 

Our argument:

1. OHS should try their hardest to give us the subjects we need to persue our careers. You have unbelievable difficulty trying to get into an acting uni without HSC drama. 
2. The fact that we only have 11 students is not a good enough reason to stunt our career choices. 
3. They're running music 2 with 3 people! But they are adding it into music 1, but it still makes it more difficult than just opening drama. DISCRIMATION AGAINST DRAMA!!!
4. They're helping out canobolas by letting their phsyics students join in with ours, because canabolas doesn't have enough. and..um..they can't even give us a drama class? 
5. We have a capable teacher who WANTS to take the class.
6. Yr 12 2003 had 13 drama students. 
7. We damn well have the right to do drama!!!

Damn School.

Just back from Syd's party...feel like writing an lj before l go to sleep. 
I wish it could have gone on longer! I love all Syd's friends, they're all so fun!
And james is so funny. :p And l still can't pin point who Gadget reminds me of. Personality wise..Jay but less creepy, Charles a tiny bit...but looks wise he reminded me of someone and l can't think of it! 
Why is it l still rant on all vainly to people? :p It's sort of a joke thats not a joke. Hehe. 
i really hope l don't get a cold from being out in the rain..
Steph better throw another party...er...TOMORROW! Yes. Thats right. Tomorrow.

Zoe seemed pretty shy for most of the night. But she warmed up to everyone eventually. I used to be like that but l'm so much more outgoing now! Especially since Lorelei took over. :p

Anywho, l have to go to sleep so l don't get sick. Will prob rant more tomorrow. :D

Dum dee dum. 

Rennie and Dad go to Egypt IN TWO DAYS! *faints*

And..and..

Trials are in 3 WEEKS!

and..and..I want Brayden. *pouts*

My god! Grace has a new layout! *shocked faces* Yes. That's right. 

Huzzah!

Do you like my little icon thingy's in the right hand corner? Of course you do!..They may be a bit confusing...but if you just hold there for a while it'll say what it is. 
The bow (reply) is because your comments are like gifts!!

And l'm in a bit of a drunk mood. 

When l look at the layout..it looks a bit sad/depressed..yes? well..i'm not sad/depressed. I just wanted a colour change. And l can even have a different av for every update! Woot! But the av's look sad too. :p Hmm..

Hmm..l think l need more lj friends. *much nodding*

Anywho, l best be off. No school tomorrow! Only peer support training! 

HAPPY BIRTHDAY FOR TOMORROW, SYD-AMAGOO!!!

I got into peer support! *woots* Supposedly Mrs Paine told Mrs Lil how good l was. She's so lovely. :p So thursday and friday (syd's birthday!) l'll be at untiting church doing my peer support training. And l have to miss out on the greek banquet. :(

Umm..highlights of today? 
I'm thinking of joining as a reserve on the yr 10 debating team, even though l don't want to anymore. :p And..umm..hmm. I was joke-arguing with zoe all day. :p and ended up writing 'zoe drinks he own pee' on the desks in maths. :D

And..there were these really odd boys, you know how you do that thing where one person puts there arms behind their back, and another person stands behind them and have to be their arms? 
Well there were these two yr 11 guys, one had his arms in his jumper and the other was standing behind him with his arms through the arm holes (looked really odd) and l was walking through the yr 11 area and...they came up to me, zoe and rosemary and pointed to me, and then hugged me. And l was taken by surprise and shocked, and then he pointed in another direction and said 'leave!' so l was laughing and walking off...and then he followed me and everytime l went to laugh or talk he would touch my nose and go 'shh' - and l was cacking my self. Then he left it with 'hug me'. So l hugged him. and he told me to leave, so l left..and everyone around was hysterical, like me. it was so odd. And funny.

And, l heard off Rachel, that these 6 kinross boys caugh chlymidia of this one OHS girl. And l'm like..6 boys caught it off one girl?! What?! and supposedly it's going through kinross, canobolas, OHS and Shean, year 10-12 and some year 9's. I don't know if it's true..but its the gossip l got from Rachel. So no sleeping around!

Anyway...YAY! I don't have any tests...scheduled. They're all over for..atleast a bit! Cos l have my trials in 4 WEEKS. and it's just revision now, basically. 

Trimester ends this week..l hope l get changed english classes, which l won't be. Cos they don't change anyone..

Anywho, l best be off.

edit: 

ARGH! i Hate people!!!!! I can't believe the story rennie just told me!
Claire and Kristy, rennie's friends, were at the servo on friday night - and they saw this 13 yearold girl run past them and hide somewhere, followed by these two seventeen yearold girls..and they found her..and just grabbed her and started bashing her up! One of them was Molly from yr 11, who is a big skank..but l mean. ARgh! They were like..bashing her head into a brick wall..and broke her nose, and finally when this 13 yearold was lying in a pool of her own blood (while molly was still kicking her in the face) Claire and Kristy went to go call the police and when the police came, they ran away! And the girl looked half dead! If they had have kept on going they could have killed her! The ambulence people said she would be alright, she just lost a lot of blood...
but argh! I'm digusted, and angry and what a stupid frigging whore! 
I didn't know the girl...but it just makes me so mad that these sort of things happen! Luckily Claire and Kristy got to fill out a statement to the police..and there were heaps of witnesses...so she might get sent to juvi..forever..

Argh!
